HEADWORD: Conducible
<hw>Con*du"ci*ble</hw> <pr>(k⟦ocr⟧n*d⟦umac⟧"s⟦icr⟧*b'l)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>conducibilis</ets>.]</ety> <def>Conducive;
