<p><q>All his laws are in themselves <qex>conducible</qex> to the
temporal interest of them that observe them.</q>
<rj><qau>Bentley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Conducibleness</ent>⟦br⟧
